subtitleNullable: Quick awareness  is the key to stop spread of this Low risk Epidemic
descriptionNullable:
An ongoing outbreak of the viral disease monkeypox was confirmed in May 2022, beginning with a cluster of cases found in the United Kingdom. 
The first confirmed case was traced to an individual with travel links to Nigeria and was detected on 6 May 2022.
During the early stages of outbreaks, obtaining reliable, synthesised data on the characteristics of cases is a challenge, especially at a global scale.
